ecef version 1.00
=================

ecef.pm contains functions to calculate ecef coordinates (earth centered earth
fixed) from latitude, longitude and height information

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

Math::Big
Math::BigFloat

